
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-netlmm-nohost-ps-05.txt'>
    <title>"Problem Statement for Network-based Localized Mobility Management", James  Kempf</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-netlmm-nohost-ps-05.txt</link>
    <description>Localized mobility management is a well understood concept in the IETF with a number of solutions already available. This document looks at the principal shortcomings of the existing solutions, all of which involve the host in mobility management, and makes a case for network-based local mobility management.</description>
    <dc:date>2006-09-24T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
